<p>1. That space bends itself into an infinitely dense point mass particle which powers AGN jets</p>
<p>or</p>
<p>2.  Taking the known behavior of charged plasma in the laboratory and deducing a circuit theory mechanism for the observed behavior of AGN jets</p>
