    <li class="comment odd alt depth-5" id="dsq-comment-7390">
        <div id="dsq-comment-header-7390" class="dsq-comment-header">
            <cite id="dsq-cite-7390">
http://fascistsoup.com/                <span id="dsq-author-user-7390">Michael Suede</span>
