            <div id="dsq-comment-message-9536" class="dsq-comment-message"><p>&#8220;A quick browse through any of the main-stream Astro-physical publications/forums etc will prove beyond a doubt that Mr Corda&#8217;s statement is correct.&#8221;</p>
